{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1000,"text":"When I saw a piece of technology called Kinect --"},{"time":4000,"text":"it was called Natal -- I was inspired,"},{"time":7000,"text":"and I thought for a moment,"},{"time":9000,"text":"maybe it's possible"},{"time":11000,"text":"to address that one problem of storytelling,"},{"time":14000,"text":"to create a character"},{"time":17000,"text":"which seemed alive,"},{"time":19000,"text":"which noticed me,"},{"time":21000,"text":"that could look me in the eyes"},{"time":23000,"text":"and feel real,"},{"time":25000,"text":"and sculpt a story about our relationship."},{"time":28000,"text":"And so a year ago,"},{"time":31000,"text":"I showed this off"},{"time":33000,"text":"at a computer show called E3."},{"time":36000,"text":"And this was a piece of technology"},{"time":38000,"text":"with someone called Claire interacting with this boy."},{"time":41000,"text":"And there was a huge row online"},{"time":44000,"text":"about, \"Hey, this can't be real.\""},{"time":47000,"text":"And so I waited till now"},{"time":49000,"text":"to have an actual demo"},{"time":51000,"text":"of the real tech."}]},{"cues":[{"time":53000,"text":"Now, this tech incorporates"},{"time":55000,"text":"three big elements."},{"time":57000,"text":"The first is a Kinect camera,"},{"time":59000,"text":"which will be out in November,"},{"time":62000,"text":"some incredible AI"},{"time":64000,"text":"that was hidden in the dusty vaults,"},{"time":67000,"text":"collecting dust"},{"time":69000,"text":"in Microsoft,"},{"time":71000,"text":"plus our quite crude"},{"time":73000,"text":"attempts at AI"},{"time":75000,"text":"at a company called Lionhead,"},{"time":78000,"text":"mixing all those things together"},{"time":80000,"text":"just to get to this one simple idea:"},{"time":83000,"text":"to create a real, living"},{"time":86000,"text":"being in a computer."},{"time":88000,"text":"Now, I'll be honest with you"},{"time":91000,"text":"and say that most of it"},{"time":93000,"text":"is just a trick,"},{"time":95000,"text":"but it's a trick that actually works."}]},{"cues":[{"time":98000,"text":"So why don't we go over and have"},{"time":100000,"text":"a look at the demo now."},{"time":102000,"text":"This is Dimitri."},{"time":104000,"text":"Dimitri, just waggle your arm around."},{"time":107000,"text":"Now, you notice he's sitting."},{"time":109000,"text":"There are no controllers,"},{"time":111000,"text":"no keyboards,"},{"time":113000,"text":"or mice,"},{"time":115000,"text":"or joysticks, or joypads."},{"time":118000,"text":"He is just going to use"},{"time":120000,"text":"his hand, his body and his voice,"},{"time":123000,"text":"just like humans interact with their hands, body and voice."}]},{"cues":[{"time":126000,"text":"So let's move forward."},{"time":128000,"text":"You're going to meet Milo for the first time."},{"time":132000,"text":"We had to give him a problem"},{"time":134000,"text":"because when we first created Milo,"},{"time":136000,"text":"we realized that he came across as a little bit of a brat,"},{"time":138000,"text":"to be honest with you."},{"time":140000,"text":"He was quite a know-it-all,"},{"time":142000,"text":"and he wanted to kind of make you laugh."},{"time":144000,"text":"So the problem we introduced to him was this:"},{"time":146000,"text":"he's just moved house."},{"time":148000,"text":"He's moved from London"},{"time":150000,"text":"to New England, over in America."},{"time":153000,"text":"His parents are too busy"},{"time":155000,"text":"to listen to his problems,"},{"time":157000,"text":"and that's when he starts almost conjuring you up."},{"time":160000,"text":"So here he is"},{"time":162000,"text":"walking through the grass."},{"time":164000,"text":"And you're able to interact with his world."},{"time":167000,"text":"The cool thing is, what we're doing"},{"time":170000,"text":"is we're changing the mind"},{"time":172000,"text":"of Milo constantly."},{"time":174000,"text":"That means no two people's Milos"},{"time":177000,"text":"can be the same."},{"time":179000,"text":"You're actually sculpting a human being here."},{"time":184000,"text":"So, he's discovering the garden."},{"time":186000,"text":"You're helping him discover the garden"},{"time":188000,"text":"by just pointing out these snails."},{"time":192000,"text":"Very simple at the start."},{"time":194000,"text":"By the way, if you are a boy, it's snails;"},{"time":197000,"text":"if you're a girl, it's butterflies"},{"time":200000,"text":"because what we found was that girls hate snails."}]},{"cues":[{"time":203000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":209000,"text":"So remember, this is the first time you've met him,"},{"time":212000,"text":"and we really want to draw you in and make you more curious."},{"time":217000,"text":"His face, by the way,"},{"time":219000,"text":"is fully AI-driven."},{"time":221000,"text":"We have complete control over his blush responses,"},{"time":224000,"text":"the diameter of his nostrils"},{"time":227000,"text":"to denote stress."},{"time":229000,"text":"We actually do something called body matching."},{"time":231000,"text":"If you're leaning forward,"},{"time":233000,"text":"he will try and slightly change"},{"time":235000,"text":"the neuro-linguistic nature of his face,"},{"time":238000,"text":"because we went out with this strong idea:"},{"time":240000,"text":"how can we make you believe that something's real?"},{"time":243000,"text":"Now we've used the hand."},{"time":245000,"text":"The other thing to use is your body."},{"time":248000,"text":"Why not just, instead of pushing left and right"},{"time":251000,"text":"with a mouse or with a joypad,"},{"time":254000,"text":"why not use your body just to lean on the chair --"},{"time":256000,"text":"again, relaxed?"},{"time":258000,"text":"You can lean back,"},{"time":260000,"text":"but the camera will change its perspective"},{"time":262000,"text":"depending on which way you're looking."}]},{"cues":[{"time":266000,"text":"So Dimitri's now going to use --"},{"time":268000,"text":"he's used his hand; he's used his body."},{"time":270000,"text":"He's now going to use the other thing which is essential,"},{"time":273000,"text":"and that's his voice."},{"time":275000,"text":"Now, the thing about voice is,"},{"time":277000,"text":"our experience with voice recognition"},{"time":279000,"text":"is pretty awful, isn't it?"},{"time":281000,"text":"It never works."},{"time":283000,"text":"You order an airline ticket; you end up in Timbuktu."},{"time":287000,"text":"So we've tackled that problem,"},{"time":289000,"text":"and we've come up with a solution, which we'll see in a second."}]},{"cues":[{"time":292000,"text":"Milo: I could just squish it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":294000,"text":"Peter Molyneux: What are you going to do, Dimitri?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":296000,"text":"Female Voice: Squashing a snail may not seem important,"},{"time":298000,"text":"but remember, even this choice"},{"time":300000,"text":"will affect how Milo develops."},{"time":303000,"text":"Do you want Milo to squash it?"},{"time":305000,"text":"When you see the microphone,"},{"time":307000,"text":"say ... (PM: Squash.) ... yes to decide."}]},{"cues":[{"time":309000,"text":"Dimitri: Go on, Milo. Squash it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":312000,"text":"PM: No. That's the wrong thing to do."},{"time":314000,"text":"Now look at his response."},{"time":316000,"text":"He said, \"Go on, Milo. Squash it.\""},{"time":319000,"text":"What we're using there is,"},{"time":321000,"text":"we're using something, a piece of technology called Tellme."},{"time":323000,"text":"It's a company that Microsoft acquired some years ago."},{"time":326000,"text":"We've got a database of words which we recognize."},{"time":328000,"text":"We pick those words out."},{"time":330000,"text":"We also reference that"},{"time":332000,"text":"with the tonation database"},{"time":334000,"text":"that we build up of Dimitri's voice,"},{"time":337000,"text":"or the user's voice."},{"time":339000,"text":"Now we need to have a bit more engagement,"},{"time":342000,"text":"and again, what we can do"},{"time":344000,"text":"is we can look at the body."},{"time":346000,"text":"And we'll do that in a second."}]},{"cues":[{"time":348000,"text":"Milo: I wonder how deep it is."},{"time":358000,"text":"Deep."}]},{"cues":[{"time":361000,"text":"PM: Okay. So what we're going to do now"},{"time":363000,"text":"is teach Milo to skim stones."},{"time":366000,"text":"We're actually teaching him."},{"time":368000,"text":"It's very, very interesting"},{"time":370000,"text":"that men, more than women,"},{"time":372000,"text":"tend to be more competitive here."},{"time":375000,"text":"They're fine with teaching Milo for the first few throws,"},{"time":378000,"text":"but then they want to beat Milo,"},{"time":380000,"text":"where women,"},{"time":382000,"text":"they're more nurturing about this."},{"time":388000,"text":"Okay, this is skimming stones."},{"time":390000,"text":"How do you skim stones?"},{"time":393000,"text":"You stand up,"},{"time":396000,"text":"and you skim the stone."},{"time":398000,"text":"It's that simple."},{"time":400000,"text":"Just recognizing your body,"},{"time":402000,"text":"recognizing the body's motions, the tech,"},{"time":404000,"text":"understanding that you've gone"},{"time":406000,"text":"from sitting down to standing up."},{"time":409000,"text":"Again, all of this is done"},{"time":411000,"text":"in the way us humans do things,"},{"time":413000,"text":"and that's crucially important"},{"time":416000,"text":"if we want Milo to appear real."}]},{"cues":[{"time":418000,"text":"Female Voice: See if you can inspire him to do any better."},{"time":426000,"text":"Try hitting the boat."}]},{"cues":[{"time":430000,"text":"Milo: Ahhh. So close."}]},{"cues":[{"time":438000,"text":"PM: That's Dimitri at his most competitive."},{"time":440000,"text":"Now beaten an 11-year-old child. Well done."}]},{"cues":[{"time":444000,"text":"Milo: Okay."}]},{"cues":[{"time":447000,"text":"PM: So, Milo's being called back in by his parents,"},{"time":450000,"text":"giving us time to be alone"},{"time":452000,"text":"and to help him out."},{"time":454000,"text":"Basically -- the bit that we missed at the start --"},{"time":456000,"text":"his parents had asked him to clean up his room."},{"time":459000,"text":"And we're going to help him with this now."},{"time":461000,"text":"But this is going to be an introduction,"},{"time":463000,"text":"and this is all about the deep psychology that we're trying to use."},{"time":466000,"text":"We're trying to introduce you"},{"time":468000,"text":"to what I believe is the most wonderful part,"},{"time":471000,"text":"you being able to talk"},{"time":473000,"text":"in your natural voice to Milo."},{"time":476000,"text":"Now, to do that, we needed a set up,"},{"time":478000,"text":"like a magician's trick."},{"time":480000,"text":"And what we did was,"},{"time":482000,"text":"we needed to give Milo this big problem."}]},{"cues":[{"time":484000,"text":"So as Dimitri"},{"time":487000,"text":"starts tidying up,"},{"time":489000,"text":"you can overhear a conversation"},{"time":491000,"text":"that Milo's having with his parents."}]},{"cues":[{"time":493000,"text":"Milo's Mom: Oh, you've got gravy all over the floor. (Milo: I didn't mean to!)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":495000,"text":"Milo's Mom: That carpet is brand new."}]},{"cues":[{"time":497000,"text":"PM: So he's just spilled"},{"time":499000,"text":"a plate of sausages on the floor,"},{"time":501000,"text":"on the brand-new carpet."},{"time":503000,"text":"We've all done it as parents; we've all done it as children."},{"time":506000,"text":"Now's a chance for Dimitri"},{"time":508000,"text":"to kind of reassure and calm Milo down."},{"time":510000,"text":"It's all been too much for him."},{"time":512000,"text":"He's just moved house. He's got no friends."},{"time":515000,"text":"Now is the time"},{"time":517000,"text":"when we open that portal"},{"time":519000,"text":"and allow you to talk to Milo."}]},{"cues":[{"time":522000,"text":"Female Voice: Why don't you try saying something encouraging"},{"time":525000,"text":"to cheer Milo up."}]},{"cues":[{"time":527000,"text":"Dimitri: Come on, Milo. You know what parents are like."},{"time":529000,"text":"They're always getting stressed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":533000,"text":"Milo: What do they want to come here for anyway?"},{"time":537000,"text":"We don't know anyone."}]},{"cues":[{"time":540000,"text":"Dimitri: Well, you've got a new school to go to."},{"time":542000,"text":"You're going to meet loads of cool, new friends."},{"time":547000,"text":"Milo: I just really miss my old house, that's all."}]},{"cues":[{"time":553000,"text":"Dimitri: Well, this is a pretty awesome house, Milo."},{"time":555000,"text":"You've got a cool garden to play in and a pond."}]},{"cues":[{"time":562000,"text":"Milo: It was good skimming stones."},{"time":572000,"text":"This looks nice."},{"time":575000,"text":"You cleaned up my room."},{"time":577000,"text":"Thanks."}]},{"cues":[{"time":579000,"text":"PM: So after three-quarters of an hour,"},{"time":581000,"text":"he recognizes you."},{"time":583000,"text":"And I promise you, if you're sitting in front of this screen,"},{"time":586000,"text":"that is a truly wonderful moment."},{"time":589000,"text":"And we're ready now"},{"time":591000,"text":"to tell a story about his childhood and his life,"},{"time":593000,"text":"and it goes on,"},{"time":595000,"text":"and he has, you know, many adventures."},{"time":597000,"text":"Some of those adventures are a little bit dark or on the darker side."},{"time":600000,"text":"Some of those adventures are wonderfully encouraging --"},{"time":602000,"text":"he's got to go to school."}]},{"cues":[{"time":604000,"text":"The cool thing is"},{"time":606000,"text":"that we're doing as well:"},{"time":608000,"text":"as you interact with him,"},{"time":610000,"text":"you're able to put things into his world; he recognizes objects."},{"time":613000,"text":"His mind is based in a cloud."},{"time":616000,"text":"That means Milo's mind,"},{"time":618000,"text":"as millions of people use it,"},{"time":620000,"text":"will get smarter and cleverer."},{"time":622000,"text":"He'll recognize more objects"},{"time":624000,"text":"and thus understand more words."}]},{"cues":[{"time":626000,"text":"But for me,"},{"time":628000,"text":"this is a wonderful opportunity"},{"time":630000,"text":"where technology, at last, can be connected with,"},{"time":633000,"text":"where I am no longer restrained"},{"time":635000,"text":"by the finger I hold in my hand --"},{"time":637000,"text":"as far as a computer game's concerned --"},{"time":639000,"text":"or by the blandness of not being noticed"},{"time":641000,"text":"if you're watching a film or a book."},{"time":644000,"text":"And I love those revolutions,"},{"time":647000,"text":"and I love the future that Milo brings."}]},{"cues":[{"time":649000,"text":"Thank you very much indeed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":651000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}